station manager
Homonym Number:
Word Class:noun
Sense Number: 1
Definition:an overseer, employer and principal worker of staff on a station, usually with the full responsibility of an absentee owner.
Origin:[none]
Register:
Register 2:
Flag: Farm Words
Domain:Rural
